UID:e80502e2ee4dd028@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Podcast - IDSA
DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: Let's Talk ID] Duration: 1522\n\nPaul Sax\, MD\, FID
 SA sits down with comedy-writer\, Mike Reiss\, and his wife\, Denise Reiss
 \, to discuss a lifetime of travel experiences spanning more than 100 coun
 tries. From submarine dives and whale sharks to a hospitalization caused b
 y Shigella\, they recount remarkable adventures and the health risks that 
 can emerge when exploring the world.\n\nEvent URL: https://www.buzzsprout.
 com/2019912/episodes/19302826-when-adventure-meets-infectious-diseases.mp3
 \n\nSource: idsa_podcast
