SUMMARY:Beyond the Brush
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260720T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260720T200000
DTSTAMP:20260624T071233Z
UID:ccb803051dfd4538@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Class/Seminar
DESCRIPTION:While most of us were taught that brushing twice a day and flo
 ssing (when we remember) was how we take care of our teeth\, modern scienc
 e reveals that maintaining oral health is about far more than just a quick
  scrub and snap.\n\nOral health is the gateway to your overall systemic we
 llness\, and effective oral hygiene is a big part of that puzzle. If you a
 re looking to elevate your daily routine from a chore to an intentional se
 lf-care ritual for overall wellness\, then this webinar is for you!\n\nWe 
 will start with the essentials\, demystifying the foundational habits of e
 ffective at-home care. You will learn the "why" behind traditional techniq
 ues before we pivot into the cutting-edge world of dental innovation.\n\nW
 e will navigate the ever-growing “dental care” aisle of the pharmacy t
 ogether\, breaking down smart ingredients\, modern technologies and innova
 tions\, and our deeper understanding of the oral microbiome - how to balan
 ce the "good" bacteria in your mouth for fresher breath and stronger ename
 l.\n\nWhether you are looking to reverse years of sensitivity\, prevent fu
 ture dental work\, or simply understand the labels on your products\, this
  course provides the clarity you need. By the end\, you’ll have a person
 alized\, tech-forward toolkit to maintain a radiant smile for a lifetime.\
 n\nThis class will be recorded and a one-week link to the recording will b
 e shared with all registered participants. \n\nTo receive incentive points
 \, attend at least 80% of the live session or listen to the entire recordi
 ng within one week.\n\nRequest disability accommodations and access info.\
 n\n\n\nClass details are subject to change.\n\nEvent URL: https://events.s
 tanford.edu/event/beyond-the-brush\n\nSource: stanford_virtual
